et": {"title_area": {"text": "官方回应婆婆杀害儿媳 3 只狗「已出警并进行教育劝导」，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，女子称养的 3 只狗被婆婆杀害引发关注。据报道，江苏南京一女子发视频称，养的三只泰迪被婆婆关在阳台砍死，后悔将婆婆接来自己家住，自己已报警。4 月 15 日，当事人告诉中国新闻周刊，「老公让我婆婆搬走了，我永远都不想看见她。」 据其介绍，平时和婆婆关系不太好，婆婆觉得狗影响孩子学习和健康，并不清楚事发时的具体情况，「我当时不在家，她跟我老公说狗咬了她，跑掉了。我找了好久，后来调监控才知道」。 对此，南京市溧水区政府工作人员回应中国新闻周刊，警方已第一时间出警，进行教育劝导，此事属于个人行为。 （中国新闻周刊）官方回应婆婆杀害儿媳 3 只狗：已出警并进行教育劝导 _ 中国 _ 老公 _ 南京"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-91978159cc32f44394f509afd6c8a855_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653102599"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI3tLTiOW+5q08EAMaCTEwNzQxMTU0OCCdx/ewBjAAOO8BQAxyCTY1MzEwMjU5OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1713316569.368152", "card_id": "Q_653043411", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 100}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "香港金像奖第六次给梁朝伟颁影帝反映了什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed57d4f573ce109ccc05445feb4727a2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653043411"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI3tLTiOW+5q08EAMaCTEwNzM5ODM2NiDdzfSwBjAAOJkBQA1yCTY1MzA0MzQxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1713316569.368527", "card_id": "Q_635303587", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhi